Paper: hep-th/9811114

Date: 1998-11-12

Title: Axial Anomaly through Analytic Regularization

Authors: L. A. Manzoni, B. M. Pimentel and J. L. Tomazelli

Comments: 8 pages, LaTeX, no figures

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A14 (1999) 177-184

In this work we consider the 2-point Green's functions in (1+1) dimensionalquantum electrodynamics and show that the correct implementation of analyticregularization gives a gauge invariant result for the vaccum polarizationamplitude and the correct coefficient for the axial anomaly.